    "name": "樹上の孤鳥",
    "steam_appid": 3158450,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>“My best friend left me nothing.</strong>”</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158450/extras/eabf0d55a64399e71f6583e1b6e82b16.avif?t=1770821143\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158450/extras_big/eabf0d55a64399e71f6583e1b6e82b16.webp?t=1770821143 width=1560 height=1560 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>＜Story＞</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The main character visits the country town of Fußdorf in search of the scenery his/her best friend wanted to show him/her before his/her death. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There, he/she meets “Chris” who resembles his/her best friend, and his/her heart is shaken.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But Chris has secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The truth is covered up with distorted good intentions. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is an unforgettable 13 days that will pierce the heart of the main character.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158450/extras/4d67d15b7ba7be6c74721b1c01327c68.avif?t=1770821143\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158450/extras_big/4d67d15b7ba7be6c74721b1c01327c68.webp?t=1770821143 width=1560 height=582 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>＜Features of this game＞</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique gender selection system</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The four characters have both male and female genders. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Two of the four characters, including the main character, can choose their gender, while the other two are determined by the main character's choice of gender.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The main storyline does not change significantly depending on the combination of genders chosen, but the content of conversations and some relationships between the characters will change. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▼ Main character R（ Rudolf / Regina ) </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158450/extras/31e9dcfe2a618a759e1f969ed08d214c.avif?t=1770821143\" width=800 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▼ Resident C ( Chris / Chris )</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158450/extras/cac6f3ebf35b45b6f5612866363ecd4c.avif?t=1770821143\" width=800 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▼ Resident H ( Hugo / Helene ) </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158450/extras/a3c3dd77482e960a26360c656ca1afb4.avif?t=1770821143\" width=800 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▼ Best friend J ( Johannes / Johanna ) </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158450/extras/29416652a2d0e7dcf015e191198fcbfc.avif?t=1770821143\" width=800 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Truth Revealed by Repeating &quot;Main Story&quot; and &quot;Past Story&quot; </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game has a “Main Story” and a “Past Story”.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In “Main Story”, the main character spends 13 days with the residents in the country town of Fußdorf.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > “Past Story”  begins by reading a diary about the days with his/her best friend who died. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is exploration and choice in the “Main Story”, but not in the “Past Story”. Days gone by consists only of conversational events.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▼ “Main Story”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158450/extras/6ae0efd434007942c8b119a6600b8f46.avif?t=1770821143\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158450/extras_big/6ae0efd434007942c8b119a6600b8f46.webp?t=1770821143 width=1560 height=873 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▼ “Past Story”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158450/extras/13e275358744c1341c9b9ac111941b35.avif?t=1770821143\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158450/extras_big/13e275358744c1341c9b9ac111941b35.webp?t=1770821143 width=1560 height=873 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >By reading both the “Main Story” and the “Past Story,” players will discover the truth behind the death of his/her best friend and the secrets of the residents who have been keeping secrets from them.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The ending of the story changes depending on the level of trust<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158450/extras/246794cc368de4d6ad45eba0a82a8094.avif?t=1770821143\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158450/extras_big/246794cc368de4d6ad45eba0a82a8094.webp?t=1770821143 width=1560 height=873 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some characters have a “trust level” that is changed by the choices they make in the story. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This trust level is determined by the cumulative total of the values set in the choices, and the ending of the story changes according to this value.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The trust level may increase, decrease, or remain the same regardless of which of the two options you choose. Trust your instincts and make your choice.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >_Even if the main character ends up in any way, he/she will never see his/her best friend again.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
